msgstr ""

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Patchwork"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Patchwork'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You can conveniently change your body. Although it will be slightly weaker "
